---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — CycleWise">
  <div class="page-wrap prose" style="max-width:680px;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: June 14, 2026</em></p>
    <h2>Data we collect</h2>
    <p>CycleWise stores cycle data (last period date, cycle length) exclusively in your browser's <strong>localStorage</strong>. This data never leaves your device and is never transmitted to our servers.</p>
    <p>If you purchase Pro access, Stripe processes your payment. We receive a confirmation token but no payment details. Your email and card information are handled entirely by Stripe.</p>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>We may use Cloudflare Analytics (privacy-preserving, no cookies) to understand general traffic patterns. No personal data is collected through analytics.</p>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We do not use tracking cookies. Pro access is stored in your browser's localStorage.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions: <a href="mailto:hello@cyclewise.app">hello@cyclewise.app</a></p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h1 { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .prose em { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 14px; display: block; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .prose h2 { margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .prose p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .prose a { color: var(--pink); }
</style>
